  "texts": [
    "To help the participants delineate the authoring process and reflect on their choices, we selected questions from our interview guide that focused on topics drawn from prior literature and user studies.",
    "These topics included visualization authoring processes, user roles in workflows, and criteria for evaluating tools [3,4,17,25].",
    "The following are the topics with example questions:• Goals: What was the goal of creating this visualization?• Ideation Process: How did you get an idea of what to visualize?",
    "• Workflow and Tasks: Can you describe the step-by-step process you follow in creating the visualization(s)?",
    "• Tools: What tools do you use, and what are their limitations (if any) in the process?"
  ],
  "correct_citations": [
    "These topics included visualization authoring processes, user roles in workflows, and criteria for evaluating tools [3,4,17,25]."
  ]
}